document.topic_text: World record siamtu Rahimov Kazakhstan tlangval ritchawi chak Nijat Rahimov chuan Rio Olympic weightlifting 77kg category-ah a pumpuiah 379kg chawiin world record thar a siam a, an ram tan gold medal a hlawh hhuak bawk. Kum 22-a upa Rahimov hian clean and jerk final-ah 214kg a chawi a, kum 15 chhung record lo awm tawh 210kg a khum chiah. China tlangval Lyu Xiaojun chu pahnihna niin Egypt aṭanga Rio pantu Mohamed Mahmoud chu pathumna a ni. Share this Post
